product_keywords: Powered Hernia Mesh Fixation Device Absorbable- 15 tacks Powered tacker offer is smart choice for faster, secure mesh fixation. Inline handle design with rubber grip. Powered hernia mesh fixation device absorbable tacks made from Polyglycolide-Co-Lactide (PGLA). It is screw-shaped hook design to ensure strong fixation, with each device containing 15 tacks.
